The source code of main tools used in Bitcoin "non-malware-based" attacks.

## Tools list:

# Misc tools

- Double Spender

# Private Key Harvesters

- Electrum cracker

- Brainflayer

- Bruteforce Wallet

- Wallet Collision

- ECDSA Private Key Recovery

- Large Bitcoin Collider Pool Script


